headline: Comcast Connecting Homes and Businesses in Greenwood, SC to Reliable, High-Speed Internet
summary: Comcast has completed an American Rescue Plan Act State and Local Fiscal Recovery Funds grant expansion project, with a $6.1 million program subsidy, in Greenwood, South Carolina. The network expansion brings Internet, mobile and security services from Xfinity and Comcast Business to residents and businesses for the first time.

headline: Think You're A Trivia Whiz? NBC's 'Win Win' Pays You To Play From Home
summary: Game shows have remained incredibly popular with television viewers over the years and one of the reasons that new shows keep getting launched by media and streaming companies. For all the people who have played along to a trivia game like "Jeopardy!" at home and answered questions for $0, there's a new game show that could make it pay to watch along.
